Package com.gsm.model

Class AuditableEntity

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.gsm.model.AuditableEntity
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    BOMTemplate, BOMTemplateDetail, Customer, Fabric, FabricColor, MaterialGroup, OrderBOM, OrderBOMDetail, Product, ProductionOutput, ProductVariant, PurchaseOrder, PurchaseOrderDetail, SaleOrder, SaleOrderDetail, Supplier, Trim, TrimVariant, User
    @MappedSuperclass
public abstract class AuditableEntity
extends java.lang.Object
    An abstract base class for entities that require auditing information. By extending this class, an entity will automatically inherit fields for tracking creation and modification details.

    This is enabled by the JpaAuditingConfiguration.
